data.title: A 10 NOBILE IMPORT EXPORT LLC
data.meta_description:
A 10 NOBILE IMPORT EXPORT LLC | 12 followers on LinkedIn. A 10 Nobile Import Export was established for the love of Sicily.
 
 As 2nd, 3rd, and 4th generation Sicilian Americans, our mission is to introduce family owned Sicilian vineyards wanting  to have a secure global connection.  Our search for an exceptional wines landed us at Tenuta dei Mille's winery in Menfi, Sicily in Spring 2015.
